{"tid":494250,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【乜仲有人寫聖誕卡嘅咩】想要聖誕卡嘅入","createTime":"2017-12-09T12:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T10:47:29.000Z","uid":51515,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6780a733d1e48857fad947ce4899ab30ee3c7ddc","tid":494250,"uid":51515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"話說我去買聖誕卡嘅時候 問個朋友意見<br />\n朋友：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朋友：乜呢個年代仲有人寫聖誕卡嘅咩<br />\n我：有呀 咪我囉<br />\n<br />\n無錯啦 又係我 <br />\n上年寫聖誕卡寫得好開心 <br />\n今年都買咗啲聖誕卡寫比大家 <br />\n仲買咗好多貼紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好興奮<br />\n<br />\n上年都有好多人想回郵比我 <br />\n不過唔駛啦我志在寫唔志在收 <br />\n多謝各位 連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅巴絲入去填一填form <br />\n小人會再次趕deadline截郵嗰日一次過寄<br />\n<br />\n預祝各位巴絲聖誕快樂！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cae8c63db094a149c2bda633c3f1eb51b6cf2a","tid":494250,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T12:29:59.000Z","msg":"多謝樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af67b59e5cb8abdc434329afd96f9a057f119d68","tid":494250,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"寄畀施永青 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ae184b6cefd8a64aa8100bc191a171740f1b19","tid":494250,"uid":42214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"填咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年都收過樓主絲打嘅卡，好多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s. 今年要澄清一下，我唔係巴打嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b25db879ae92